data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged.****Price improvement**** WELCOME to your MOVE-IN READY DREAM HOME in Weeki Wachee, FL! NO HOA, CDD, OR FLOOD INSURANCE! This extra spacious 3130 sq ft gorgeous property features 4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, formal dining/flex room, den/study, 3 car garage & has a total of 3740 sq ft. & sits on almost a full 1/2 acre lot. Sellers have cleared the lot & extended driveway. Has a transferrable 2/10 Builder's Warranty. As you step inside, you will be greeted by a spacious bright open floor plan that has gorgeous Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring throughout which is waterproof, easy to care for, & easy to keep clean, designer faucets, ceiling fans throughout,& designer light fixtures. The luxury kitchen boasts a large center island with Quartz counters, wooden cabinets with soft closing doors & drawers, ample storage space, microwave, dishwasher, pantry, hanging light fixtures as well as Smart Samsung Fridge, smart double oven & smart stove, which are all stainless steel. Refrigerator has transferable warranty. The over sized Great Room has a built in floor outlet to make it easy to plug in your electrical devices for those family movie nights! The master bedroom is a retreat withthin the home, providing an oasis of comfort & relaxation. Featuring 2 large walk-in closets, ample storage space for your wardrobe & accessories. The master bathroom is a sanctuary, featuring Quartz counters, dual sinks, wood cabinets, & an oversized stand up luxury shower with 3 separate shower heads. Unwind after a long day by immersing yourself with a relaxing shower. The split floor plan offers privacy for the owner's suite!! The other side of the home are the 3 additional bedrooms & 2 additional full bathrooms, 1 bathroom w/dual sinks & tub/shower combo, & other with stand-up shower w/matching wood cabinets & updated counter tops w/LED flush lighting! Enjoy low electric bills as you have a new high-efficiency HVAC system, high-efficiency water heater, double paned windows & a well-insulated home!! New well & septic that is serviced every 6 months. The laundry room is conveniently located inside the home & steps away you'll find your interior access to the garage. Home is well insulated with R30, resulting in significantly lower utility costs. The triple garage gives ample space for parking vehicles & additional storage. To top it off, the property features a large driveway with space for numerous cars. Step outside to the lanai & fenced backyard which creates a private haven for relaxation & recreation. The fence offers peace of mind for families & pets, allowing them to freely enjoy the outdoor space. The spacious backyard is perfect for gatherings & outdoor activities. Whether you want to relax in the sun or host a barbecue w/ friends & family, this backyard is the perfect setting for all your outdoor entertainment needs.This home offers everything you need for comfortable & convenient living, both indoors & outdoors. Located in a growing area of Royal Highlands where everyone enjoys larger lots & more space between homes, & having no HOA or CDD you have the ability to park your boat, camper, & other large toys on the side or backyard! Only 10 minutes from shopping, groceries, schools, state park with a Mermaid Show & Buccaneer Bay Water Park, kayaking on Weeki Wachee River, boating, fishing, swimming with the manatees, sunsets at Pine Island, Hernando Beach, & so much more! Make this home yours today!
